{"tid":370541,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不了要返工? 9gag版文宣搞唔搞得過","createTime":"2017-08-23T05:49:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T14:25:32.000Z","uid":48213,"like":69,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea22e2ced5184cc7f8388663223b21a2a3dd29e","tid":370541,"uid":48213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:49:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x4i6no5b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx4i6no5b&h=b8b87c4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/snkh42ou\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsnkh42ou&h=d32d3165&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0yx5kpjd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0yx5kpjd&h=b5d3c10a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港搞成咁大家氣餒都好正常，但下下有咩抗爭就反帶動話&quot;不了要返工&quot; &quot;要衝 不了&quot; 更加惡性循環，無補於事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n忽發奇想可唔可以用9gag類型既文宣向外國城勢力滲透下主流意識打好個底，宣揚下 點解香港搞成咁我地一路反抗不果既事實， 香港同地獄鬼國大不同, 或甚種種被迫害事件諸如gfung拉監 dq議員等等<br />\n<br />\n真香港人可以 睇睇有咩可以改善，估到5毛會入黎屌無用，依然希望做少少實事哪怕只有半份力<br />\n<br />\n/<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/seehongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fseehongkong%2F&d=upHURH%2BY6M7wXchtIaTU5f9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0405bb13\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/seehongkong/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zd2ejasm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzd2ejasm&h=33fb9095&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"115d69c8f9d111e9a7430fbbeefd101e32cc7cab","tid":370541,"uid":48213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T05:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lftwkr10\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flftwkr10&h=da3aa52c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b063228da9e669a2d8eddf374887123560d1c0c","tid":37054